*.sqlite3-shm
google_token.json
client_secret.json
# mcpbrain/google_oauth_client.json is the SHARED desktop OAuth client. It is
# committed and bundled (private repo; a desktop client secret is non-confidential
# under Google's PKCE flow) so every install carries it. The per-user token
# (google_token.json) and the user-supplied client_secret.json stay ignored.
